<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title> Referral Code</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-[#F5F5F5] flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">

  <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-10 w-full max-w-lg text-center">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-black mb-4">Enter the Referral Code</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      Enter your friend’s referral code to unlock exclusive rewards! When you sign up using a referral code, both you
      and your friend will receive a bonus. Don’t miss out on this opportunity to start with extra benefits!
    </p>

    <form class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
      <input type="text" placeholder="11J8BC4GH1"
        class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-center focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-black">
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="bg-black text-white font-semibold py-2 px-6 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-800 transition duration-200">
        Submit
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>

</body>

</html>
